## 🐛 Bug Report

There are no borders in the cell, but when I use ExcelJS to read it, the borders appear.

Lib version: 4.4.0

## Steps To Reproduce

```javascript
  if (cell.style.border) {
        const borders = ['left', 'right', 'top', 'bottom'];
        borders.forEach(border => {
            if (cell.style.border[border]) {
                styles += `border-${border}: 1px solid black;`;
            }
        });
    }
```
